	(text "Questions:\n	- What signals do we need to digitize\n	- do we want to send the analog signals straight to the multiplexer\n	  then from the multiplexer to the edge connector? Or do we want it\n	  to go through the pico first\n	- where do we want the pico connected?\n	- what connections on the backplane pinnout correspond to the pico\n	  on the analog board?"
